name: Eagle Speedmapping Session 2 - King Double
description: The Eagle Speedmapping Sessions' goal is to make maps within a 2 (in practice 3) hour limit. In this session, 14 maps were made, and the themes were: - Knee-Deep in the Dead - Techbases, starbases - The Shores of Hell - techbases warped by Hell - Inferno - hellish environments And a bonus theme - map must have less than 750 vertex.
